Package: professorrr
Type: Package
Title: A Suite of Performance Evaluations Tools for Teachers
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Ghislain", "Gueye", "Nono", email = "nonoghislain@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A suite of tools, which allows teachers to evaluate the performance of their students.
    The package makes it easy for teachers to calculate grades with specific parameters.
    After the computation of grades, the teacher can also generate various kinds of reports.
